            "<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-blue-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7.864 4.243A7.5 7.5 0 0 1 19.5 10.5c0 2.92-.556 5.709-1.568 8.268M5.742 6.364A7.465 7.465 0 0 0 4.5 10.5a7.464 7.464 0 0 1-1.15 3.993m1.989 3.559A11.209 11.209 0 0 0 8.25 10.5a3.75 3.75 0 1 1 7.5 0c0 .527-.021 1.049-.064 1.565M12 10.5a14.94 14.94 0 0 1-3.6 9.75m6.633-4.596a18.666 18.666 0 0 1-2.485 5.33\" /></svg>",
            [
                new("What is Digi-ID?", "A passwordless authentication protocol for DigiByte. Websites show a <code>digiid://</code> QR code — you scan it with your wallet, approve the domain, and the wallet signs a cryptographic challenge. No passwords needed."),
                new("How do I use Digi-ID?", "Go to the <b>ID</b> tab → scan the Digi-ID QR code from a website (or paste the <code>digiid://</code> URI). Review the domain name, then tap <b>Approve</b>. The wallet signs the challenge and sends it to the website."),
                new("Is Digi-ID safe?", "Yes. Each website gets a unique derived key (path <code>m/13'/siteIndex'/0'/0</code>). Your main wallet keys are never exposed. Only a cryptographic signature is sent — no private data leaves your device."),
            ]),

        new("analytics", "Analytics & Market Data", "Price, market cap, network stats", "bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20",
            "<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-purple-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z\" /></svg>",
            [
                new("Where can I see the DGB price?", "Go to <b>Analytics</b> (from Settings or Home). The page shows the current DGB price in your selected fiat currency, 24h change, market cap, volume, and a 7-day sparkline chart."),
                new("Where does the price data come from?", "Prices are fetched from the CoinGecko API via a server-side proxy (to avoid browser CORS and rate limits). Data is cached for 60 seconds."),
            ]),

        new("p2p", "P2P Marketplace", "Peer-to-peer trading (coming soon)", "bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20",
            "<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-orange-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 21v-7.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h3a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75V21m-4.5 0H2.36m11.14 0H18m0 0h3.64m-1.39 0V9.349M3.75 21V9.349m0 0a3.001 3.001 0 0 0 3.75-.615A2.993 2.993 0 0 0 9.75 9.75c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a2.993 2.993 0 0 0 2.25 1.016c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.015a3.001 3.001 0 0 0 3.75.614m-16.5 0a3.004 3.004 0 0 1-.621-4.72l1.189-1.19A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 5.378 3h13.243a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.06.44l1.19 1.189a3 3 0 0 1-.621 4.72M6.75 18h3.75a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75V13.5a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H6.75a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v3.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75Z\" /></svg>",
            [
                new("What is the P2P Marketplace?", "A planned feature for buying and selling DGB directly with other users — no centralized exchange needed. It will include order matching, real-time trade chat via SignalR, and multisig escrow for safe trades."),
                new("When will it be available?", "The P2P Marketplace is planned for Q2 2026. Check the <b>Roadmap</b> page for the latest status."),
            ]),

        new("remittance", "Remittance", "Send by username, fee comparison", "bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/20",
